Class ScoreCounter.ScoreBoard

java.lang.Object
fr.sos.witchhunt.model.flow.ScoreCounter.ScoreBoard
All Implemented Interfaces:
Visitor
Enclosing class:
ScoreCounter
public class ScoreCounter.ScoreBoard extends Object implements Visitor

Internal class of ScoreCounter.

In charge of keeping accounts of the score obtained at each round by each player.

Update itselfs using the Visitor design pattern.
